{"tid":1741473,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對抗蛇齋餅粽","createTime":"2019-11-20T10:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:59:06.000Z","uid":302638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"215ca1c2a3366801b7082e60de13a9c40288e89d","tid":1741473,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"開第四次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位非p見有用可唔可以幫我推吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家屋企都有廢老收左蛇齋餅粽去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老一輩覺得收左人嘅禮物就要幫返人，呢樣野我地改變唔倒<br />\n但係我地可以做嘅係利用佢地另一樣改變唔倒嘅野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貪念<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n我地只要同啲廢老解釋返奶共班狗派野嘅目的就係要贏選舉，而佢地輸左嘅話嚟緊幾年就會派更多野想贏返下次選舉，咁班貪心嘅廢老就會自動波唔投奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位孝順嘅子孫唔係唔幫手呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da1d745636617ba83ad1ecc9eb12bede8954dba","tid":1741473,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"呢3分鐘無人睇倒就又要再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260deb23696068c9d867302a6e74cb59c998d753","tid":1741473,"uid":327469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"215ca1c2a3366801b7082e60de13a9c40288e89d","tid":1741473,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"開第四次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位非p見有用可唔可以幫我推吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家屋企都有廢老收左蛇齋餅粽去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老一輩覺得收左人嘅禮物就要幫返人，呢樣野我地改變唔倒<br />\n但係我地可以做嘅係利用佢地另一樣改變唔倒嘅野<br />\n<span style=\"colo